        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It changes the amino acid sequence of the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"A L A D\"><math alttext=\"A L A D\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>ALAD</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> protein so that the enzyme catalyzes a different reaction.</p>",
